这篇文章的主要内容

1. 获取环境信息的传感器

第一部分列举出了当前获取环境信息的所有传感器，涉及颜色相机，一般相机，激光雷达，红外相机，热相机等


2. data set

讲述了当前相关的data set，没有具体的去看，等以后用的时候再看。


3. 介绍了三种data structure

3.1 k-d tree

3.2 Octree

3.3 Panorama images


4. Plane detection

Manmade structures consist in large parts of planar regions.

The structure of indoor environments usually comprises a large amount of planar surfaces.

平面检测的方法

4.1 Plane description

4.2 Region growing

4.3 RANSAC

4.4 The 3D Hough Transform



5. Laser-based 2D mapping methods

5.1 Three laser-based 2D mapping methods

5.1.1 GMapping

using odometry infomation

5.1.2 Hector SLAM

using odometry information or inertial measurement。

5.1.3 TSD-SLAM

works completely without odometry.

5.2 Occupancy grid maps

All the above 3 mapping methods use occupancy grid maps for map representation.

